quran[14]{c,v,t,f}:
  36,82,"Chisimu chilamusi Chakwe pati asachile chindu (kuti chipatikane), agambaga kuchisalila kuti: “M’be.” Basi ni chikasaŵaga."
  36,83,"Basi kuswejela ni Kwakwe Ajula jwamuli mu Nkono Mwakwe mwana uchimwene wakuchilamulila chindu chilichose, soni Kukwakwe tinchiuchisyidwa (wosope ŵene)."
  37,67,"Kaneko chisimu akwete kupata ŵanganyao kupwatika pa chele (chitelacho) chakuwanganyichisya gagali mesi gamasemule nnope."
  37,68,"Kaneko chisimu kwakuwujila kwao ni ku Moto Waukali."
  37,69,"Chisimu ŵanganyao ŵasimene achatati ŵao ali ŵapotele."
  38,46,"Chisimu Uwwe twasagwile ŵanganyao pakwapa ndamo jambone ja kumbuchila Nyumba Jambesi (ja Akhera)."
  38,47,"Soni chisimu ŵanganyao Kukwetu ŵaliji ŵakusagulidwa soni ŵambone."
  38,48,"Soni munkumbuchilani Ismaila, Al-yasa‘a (Eliya) ni Dhul-Kifli (Yesaya), soni ŵosope ŵene ŵaliji mu ŵandu ŵambone."
  39,31,"Kaneka chisimu ŵanganyammwe lisiku lya Kiyama kwa M’mbuje gwenu (Allah) tinchiŵa nkukangana."
  39,32,"Ana nduni jwali jwalupuso nnope kwakumpunda mundu jwansepele Allah unami, ni kuikanila yakuona pati im’bichililemo? Ana ku Jahannama nganikuŵa kwiuto lya achimakafili?"
  39,33,"Sano ajula (Muhammadi ﷺ) jwaayiche ni yakuona ni ŵaijitichisye yalakweyo (maswahaba ni ŵamunyuma mwao), ŵanganyao ni ŵali ŵawoga (wakun’jogopa Allah)."
  40,10,"Chisimu aŵala ŵaŵakufuulu takaŵilanjidwe (ni kusalilidwa kuti): “Chisimu kunchima kwa Allah (kumwanchimaga jenumanja ndema jamwankanaga ku duniya) kwaliji kwekulungwa kupunda kulichima kwenu (lelo) mwachimisyene (m’Motomo). (Kumbuchilani) ndema jamwaŵilanjidwaga ku chikulupi basi jenumanja nikanaga.”"
  40,11,"Ŵanganyao tachiti: “Ambuje ŵetu! Mwatupele chiwa kaŵilikose (m’migongo ja achatati ŵetu ni panyuma pa umi wa duniya), ni ntupele umi kaŵilikose (pa duniya ni ku Akhera), basi tujitichiisye sambi syetu. Ana nipana litala lyakopochela (ku Moto kuno?” Tachisalilidwa kuti: “Pangali.)”"
  40,12,"(Tachisalilidwa kuti): “Yalakweyi niligongo lyanti ndema jajwalumbanjidwaga Allah Jikape mwakanilaga, nambo naga nkum’bwanganya Jwalakwe (ni isanamu) ni mwakulupililaga, basi chiilanyo chosope chili cha Allah Jwapenani kusyene, Jwankulungwa nnope.”"